; Unstratified aggregation (delta-relational-IR R3 stratification reject,
; v3-spec-statecell.md §5): `count_i32` summarizes `item`, but its output
; `total` is fed back into `item`, so `item` shares the aggregate's SCC and
; is not final before the aggregate runs. The Stratify pass rejects this as
; the sibling of the unstratified-negation error, in all 4 optimization
; modes, BEFORE the F14 control-flow "not yet supported" pre-pass.
#functor count_i32(aggregate i32 Val, summary i32 Count).
#message seed(i32 X).
#local item(i32 X).
#local total(i32 N).

item(X) : seed(X).
item(N) : total(N).

total(N) : count_i32(X, N) over (i32 X) { item(X) }.
